Navigate to the Project Directory

        cd /Users/nithineleti/Downloads/PROJECTS/Deep_Research_Through_an_AI_Agent_Using_OpenAI

Create a Virtual Environment

        /Library/Frameworks/Python.framework/Versions/3.13/bin/python3 -m venv venv

Activate the Virtual Environment

        source venv/bin/activate

 Install Dependencies

        pip install streamlit crewai langchain-openai python-dotenv requests reportlab pypdf

Set Up Environment Variables

        OPENAI_API_KEY=your_openai_api_key
        FIRECRAWL_KEY=your_firecrawl_api_key

Run the Application

        streamlit run deep_research_app/main.py

Access the App

        Local URL: http://localhost:8501
        Network URL: http://192.0.0.2:8501